title: Amir Talal Khan wins NA-178 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz Candidate Amir Talal Khan has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-178 Muzaffargarh-IV by securing 1,13,816 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Abdul Qayyum Khan Jatoi, who bagged 87,932 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 52.35 percent.
